Organisers of Big Brother Naija, BBNaija, has announced a twist to the reality show. Official host of BBNaija, Ebuka Obi-Uchendu during Sunday night live eviction disclosed that there would be no eviction this week. Ebuka added that there would also be no nominations by housemates even as he urged viewers to expect more surprises as from 10pm on Sunday. He added that the task for veto power will be different this Sunday too. DAILY POST reported that Khafi was evicted from the BBNaija reality show. Her eviction has left 10 housemates battling for N60m worth of prizes. Download Daily Post App.    Subscribe to Daily Post Newsletter.    Advertise with us.   Send us enquiries, press releases.